examples.en: The road skirted the lake.
She was wearing a short skirt.
The boat skirted the coast.
Stop pulling on my skirt.
We didn't go through the wood but skirted it.
examples.ru: Мы не пошли через лес, а обошли его.

examples.en: She wore a skirt with checks.
The skirt does up at the back.
The zip on my skirt had broken.
There's a piece of thread on your skirt; let me pull it off.
examples.ru: На твоей юбке нитка, дай я ее сниму.

examples.en: We skirted around the edge of the city.
The waist of this skirt is too tight.
examples.ru: Эта юбка слишком тесна в талии.

examples.en: Her long skirt billowed in the breeze.
examples.ru: Её длинная юбка развевалась на ветру.

examples.en: Do you think this shirt will go with the skirt I bought?
examples.ru: Думаешь, эта блузка подойдёт к юбке, которую я купила?

examples.en: The skirt was too big around the waist.
examples.ru: Юбка была слишком широкой в талии.

examples.en: Her skirt rustled as she walked.

examples.en: Her skirt swished as she walked.

examples.ru: На одной из сторон этой юбки имеется разрез.

examples.en: Back a skirt with stiff material.

examples.en: Her long skirt brushed the floor.

examples.en: That skirt is the absolute latest!
examples.ru: Эта юбка - абсолютная новинка! (юбка из самой новой коллекции)

examples.en: The skirt is gathered at the waist.
Liz smoothed her skirt and sat down.
She adjusted the drape of her skirt.

examples.en: Can you make this dress into a skirt?
